name: Where I Live Now
description:
Help a frog fish up things to outfit her small world.

Made for Ludum Dare 38 but I super over-scoped and took about 6 full working days (over a couple weeks) to finish. Opps. I had fun making stuff in 3d though. Pardon my glitches.

Music / SFX

  • Abishai — Ambient Piece #1
  • Rocktopus — Splash9
